Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.14,0:30:56.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,严寒改变了我们所有人  包括夜车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The freeze changed us all, the Night Car too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.05,0:31:00.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How?
